">両立支援</a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/environment/benefit/\">福利厚生・制度</a>\n            </dd>\n          </dl>\n          <dl>\n            <dt>\n              <span class=\"en\">Recruit</span>\n              <span class=\"jp\">採用情報</span>\n            </dt>\n            <dd>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/recruit/message/\">採用メッセージ</a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/recruit/\">募集要項</a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/recruit/faq/\">よくある質問</a>\n            </dd>\n          </dl>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bottom-area sp\">\n      <div class=\"c-nav\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.e2r.jp/ja/sfm2028/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link bg-blue\">MY PAGE</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.e2r.jp/ja/sfm2028/entry.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link bg-green\">ENTRY</a>\n      </div>\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"c-nav-btn\">\n        <span class=\"inn\">\n          <span class=\"line\"></span>\n          <span class=\"line\"></span>\n          <span class=\"line\"></span>\n        </span>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </div><!-- /header -->\n</header>\n    <main class=\"home\">\n\n      <section class=\"home-mv-section\">\n        <div class=\"swiper\">\n          <div class=\"txt-box\">\n            <h2 class=\"mv-ttl\">\n              <span class=\"anm-ttl-fadeInUp\">未来を動かす鍵は、</span>\n              <span class=\"second-line anm-ttl-fadeInUp\">果てなき探究心。</span>\n            </h2>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide sp-column\">\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv01-01.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv01-01-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv01-01_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv01-02.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv01-02-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv01-02_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n            <!-- slide01 -->\n\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide sp-column\">\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv02-01.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv02-01-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv02-01_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv02-02.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv02-02-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv02-02_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n            <!-- slide02 -->\n\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide sp-column\">\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-01.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-01-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-01_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-02.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-02-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-02_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n            <!-- slide03 -->\n\n\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide sp-column\">\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv04-01.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv04-01-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-01_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n              <figure>\n                <span class=\"bg\"></span>\n                <div class=\"img\">\n                  <picture>\n                    <source media=\"(min-width: 769px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/mv04-02.jpg.webp\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv04-02-sp.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                    <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/mv03-02_sp.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"> -->\n                  </picture>\n                </div>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n            <!-- slide04 -->\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n\n      <section class=\"home-follow-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-block\">\n          <h2 class=\"ttl en anm-fadeInLeft\">Follow Your Curiosity.</h2>\n          <div class=\"txt-box\">\n            <!-- <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/bg-follow.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"follow-bg\"> -->\n            <!-- <picture>\n              <source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/graduate/img/home/bg-follow.svg\">\n              <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/bg-follow-sp.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"follow-bg\">\n            </picture> -->\n            <p class=\"label en anm-fadeInUp\">Message</p>\n            <p class=\"txt anm-fadeInUp\">\n              経理・財務の仕事は<br>\n              お金を数える、確かめるだけのものではない。<br>\n              「Accounting」という言葉が示すように<br>\n              この仕事の本質は、企業価値を証明・説明し、<br>\n              未来への可能性を提示することにある。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"txt anm-fadeInUp\">\n              真のプロフェッショナルは<br>\n              常に、「数字にある背景」を突き詰めて考える。<br>\n              なぜ、その数字になったのか。<br>\n              数字から、何が見えてくるのか。<br>\n              あくなき探究心こそが、<br>\n              未来を切り拓く原動力であることを知っているからだ。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"txt anm-fadeInUp\">\n              さあ、住友商事グループの経営を<span class=\"ib\">経理・財務の力で支え、</span><br>\n              あるべき未来へと導いていこう。<br>\n              未来を読み解くための鍵は、<br>\n              いつだって、あなたの探究心にあるのだから。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"sub-ttl c-vertical-text-indent anm-fadeInUp\">\n              未来を動かす鍵は、<br>\n              果てなき探究心。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"bottom-ttl en anm-fadeInUp\">\n              Follow Your Curiosity.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-treat img-treat01 anm-fadeInLeft\">\n            <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/follow01.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-treat img-treat02 anm-fadeInLeft\">\n            <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/follow02.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-treat img-treat03 anm-fadeInLeft\">\n            <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/follow03.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"img-treat img-treat04 anm-fadeInLeft\">\n            <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/follow04.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </section>\n      <section class=\"home-company-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-block c-sec-skew\">\n          <div class=\"d-flex case--reverse\">\n            <div class=\"d-flex case--center c-bg-skew01 bg-color-company\">\n              <p class=\"label en\">Company</p>\n              <div class=\"c-ttl-area\">\n                <h2 class=\"sec-ttl\">会社を知る</h2>\n                <p class=\"txt\">私たちSFM(住友商事フィナンシャルマネジメント)が果たすべき使命、当社の概要や特長についてご紹介します。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"link-area anm-fadeInUp\">\n              <a href=\"/graduate/company/\" class=\"c-link-item\">\n                <div class=\"img-box\">\n                  <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/company01.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                <p class=\"name\">SFMについて</p>\n              </a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/number/\" class=\"c-link-item\">\n                <div class=\"anm-fadeInUp\">\n                  <div class=\"img-box\">\n                    <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/company02.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                  <p class=\"name\">数字でわかるSFM</p>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n      <section class=\"home-business-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-block c-sec-skew\">\n          <div class=\"d-flex c-bg-skew01 bg-color-business\">\n            <p class=\"label en\">Business</p>\n            <div class=\"c-ttl-area\">\n              <h2 class=\"sec-ttl\">事業を知る</h2>\n              <p class=\"txt\">未来を切り拓くために、SFMが担う経理・財務とは。<br class=\"pc\">その全体像について、主な役割やプロジェクトを通してお伝えします。</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"link-area\">\n            <a href=\"/graduate/business/\" class=\"c-link-item anm-fadeInUp\">\n              <div class=\"img-box\">\n                <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/business01.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              <p class=\"name\">事業紹介</p>\n            </a>\n\n            <a href=\"/graduate/project/\" class=\"c-link-item\">\n              <div class=\"anm-fadeInUp\">\n                <div class=\"img-box\">\n                  <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/business02.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                <p class=\"name\">プロジェクト紹介</p>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"home-work-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-block c-sec-skew\">\n          <div class=\"d-flex case--reverse\">\n            <div class=\"d-flex case--center c-bg-skew01 bg-color-work\">\n              <p class=\"label en\">Work</p>\n              <div class=\"c-ttl-area\">\n                <h2 class=\"sec-ttl\">仕事を知る</h2>\n                <p class=\"txt\">SFMでは日々どのような業務を行っているのか。<br class=\"pc\">SFMの多岐にわたる経理・財務の仕事を、２つの職種を通してご紹介します。</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"link-area\">\n              <a href=\"/graduate/work/\" class=\"c-link-item anm-fadeInUp\">\n                <div class=\"img-box\">\n                  <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/work01.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\">\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"name\">仕事を知る</p>\n              </a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"home-interview-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-block c-sec-skew\">\n          <div class=\"d-flex c-bg-skew01 bg-color-interview\">\n            <p class=\"label en anm-fadeInUp\">Interview</p>\n            <div class=\"c-ttl-area anm-fadeInUp\">\n              <h2 class=\"sec-ttl\">社員を知る</h2>\n              <p class=\"txt\">常に探究し続けるSFMの社員。<br class=\"pc\">そんなSFMの「人」を通して、仕事のやりがいや社風をお伝えします。</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"link-area\">\n            <a href=\"/graduate/interview/\" class=\"c-link-item anm-fadeInUp\">\n              <div class=\"img-box\">\n                <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/interview01.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n              <p class=\"name\">社員インタビュー Index</p>\n            </a>\n            <a href=\"/graduate/crosstalk/\" class=\"c-link-item\">\n              <div class=\"anm-fadeInUp\">\n                <div class=\"img-box\">\n                  <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/interview02.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                <p class=\"name\">クロストーク Index</p>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"home-recruit-section\">\n        <div class=\"inner-block\">\n          <div class=\"environment-area anm-fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"img-area\">\n              <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/environment.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"txt-area c-bg-skew01\">\n              <p class=\"label en\">Environment</p>\n              <h3 class=\"ttl\">働く環境</h3>\n              <p class=\"txt\">\n                未来のために安心して働ける環境を<span class=\"ib\">整えています。</span><br>SFMの働き方・制度をご紹介します。\n              </p>\n              <!-- <div class=\"link-area\"> -->\n              <a href=\"/graduate/environment/human_resource/\" class=\"c-btn01\"><span><span class=\"link-txt\">人材育成</span></span></a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/worklifebalance/\" class=\"c-btn01\"><span><span class=\"link-txt\">両立支援</span></span></a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/environment/benefit/\" class=\"c-btn01\"><span><span class=\"link-txt\">福利厚生・制度</span></span></a>\n              <!-- </div> -->\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"recruit-area anm-fadeInUp\">\n            <div class=\"img-area\">\n              <img src=\"/graduate/img/home/recruit.png.webp\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"txt-area c-bg-skew01\">\n         